snippet.title: 黒いミシン -SEKAIKEI GIRL- for MSX (2020) Full Playthrough (MiSTer FPGA MSX Core)
snippet.description:
Heard about this MSX homebrew through my long time online friend Rani Baker, who sadly passed away last week, so this playthrough and the pain in my wrist for playing this on keyboard for 2 hours are dedicated to her. RIP Rani. Get the game here: http://ags.indiesj.com/Entry/26/

Played on MiSTer FPGA, MSX core!
